edu.purdue.cs.encourse.domain

Class Project

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.purdue.cs.encourse.domain.Project

  • @Entity
public class Project
extends Object
    Represents a project that has been created by a professor. Primarily used for identifying relations involving a project, and storing general information about project.
    Author:
    William Jordan Reed, reed226@purdue.edu
